# Financial Risk Solvency Resilience Additional Risks Amount

## identifier
de5179

## type
float

## definition
Report the value of any reserves established by the Actuary in relation to additional risks or costs that are not otherwise reflected in the prescribed requirements of the solvency standard, including any transitional adjustment required.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=FinancialRisk.Solvency.ResilienceAdditionalRisks.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.05
- period=instant
